# --- Secrets / sensitive ---
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
!**/.env.*.example

# SSL certificates / private keys (DO NOT COMMIT)
**/ssl/**
**/*.pem
**/*.key

# Backups / deploy artifacts
**/backups/**
**/.deploy-tmp/**
**/*deploy*.tar.gz
**/deploy-*.log

# Logs
**/*.log

# Node / Next / React build outputs
**/node_modules/**
**/.next/**
**/out/**
**/build/**
**/dist/**

# Python caches
**/__pycache__/**
**/*.pyc
**/.pytest_cache/**

# Test / tooling outputs
**/test-results/**
**/.playwright-mcp/**
